{"tid":595800,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有時覺得00後真係好慘","createTime":"2018-03-17T04:38:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-17T04:41:01.000Z","uid":89134,"like":4,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a182bf29e6b58a3f6b0e1166c58bce28257b7e37","tid":595800,"uid":89134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T04:38:05.000Z","msg":"想當年仲記得90後比社會屌爆<br />\n<br />\n洗米係馬桶洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n裙腳仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n工作態度差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔識用excel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔識用google document<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n港女十四巴<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">大部分都係開始投身咗社會先比人插</span><br />\n<br />\n而家00後最大個班DSe中文筆試都未考已經比你地鬧緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  更何況後面個啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">你地又唔鐘意廢老插你地 但你地又學廢老插人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\n你鬧有人講蝗語 唔識陳奕迅 聽韓歌<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">好似講到90後全部都聽陳奕迅 唔聽韓歌咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n你話只係一部分唔代表全部 咁攞住呢個原則 唔通00後全部都唔識陳奕迅 只聽韓歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以偏概全 一竹竿打一船人 好咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔好唔記得00後搞成咁 係因為政府放啲大陸人入嚟生仔 同埋教育政策上親共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  洗腦教育 先搞成後面咁<br />\n你地就拉埋成堆土生土長香港人落水<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">咁玩分化法 香港人仲點團結呀？</span>"},{"pid":"953578221c5a21ff0aeb5eaa06e72ed6ca1012cd","tid":595800,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T04:39:50.000Z","msg":"慘你老母 成班蝗蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces